divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking my kids to a haunted house when I was loading them up to go all I saw was two bright orange oval shaped object coming threw the trees and going straight up.my first reaction was to scream and point. I knew it wasn't a plane cause planes don't go straight up. I took a picture and tryed to get a video but I was a little shaky and scared. I watched it till I could no longer see it and was scared out of my mind.I know this was a UFO sighting.
Summary: was oval and came up from ground so bright saw it come threw tree line
